常好奇。\r\n　　流言四起，有人说外星人进攻，有人说苏联的秘密武器，洛克威尔的平静被打破了。政府派来了专员肯曼斯莱。作为最先接触巨人的人，霍加斯和他的好朋友丁将巨人藏在了丁的旧车场。\r\n　　但是令人担心的谣言越来越烈－状况十分险峻，洛克威尔人心惶惶。霍加斯向他的巨人朋友求助将小镇从自己制造的恐慌和偏激中拯救出来，而巨人也找到了自己的人性。总会有一些时候，你能够真正发现你的朋友－即使有时候它只是金属。　　 ","name":"The Iron Giant","name_cn":"钢铁巨人","tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":54,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机器人","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1999","count":30,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":30,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萝卜","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"牺牲","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"反战","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"拯救世界","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"友情","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"华纳","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电影","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"90年代","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"非日本动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1999年8月","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"艾力·马伦斯奥","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SF","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"想看","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"钢铁巨人","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"范·迪塞尔","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"布拉德·伯德","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"正常向","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1990s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1990-1999","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小说改","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"喜剧","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"钢铁巨人"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1999年8月6日"},{"key":"片长","value":"86分钟"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"http://www.irongiant.com/"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"原作","value":"Ted Hughes"},{"key":"导演","value":"Brad Bird"},{"key":"脚本","value":"Tim McCanlies、Brad Bird"},{"key":"制片人","value":"Allison Abbate、Des McAnuff"},{"key":"音乐","value":"Michael Kamen"},{"key":"发行","value":"Warner Bros. Entertainment, Inc"}],"rating":{"rank":1329,"total":186,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":4,"5":3,"6":25